Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 21:26:58 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] ADD review-completion prompts for patch-agent done
 decisions

Track clean-review completion state on patch-agent chats so the terminal highlights the reviewed feature, asks for a yes/no decision, consumes yes locally, and reopens the agent session when later chat text arrives.
